      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/general-atlantic-said-to-near-stake-purchase-in-tech-firm-kyriba</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泛大西洋资本集团同意从 Bridgepoint Group Plc 手中收购美国财务管理软件提供商 Kyriba Corp. 的少数股权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/general-atlantic-said-to-near-stake-purchase-in-tech-firm-kyriba</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 20:08:03 GMT</pubDate>
